{"tid":868349,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"盧卡古：我會超越亨利在英超的進球紀錄","createTime":"2018-10-19T11:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T11:40:18.000Z","uid":124292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c28b811a834bfa31a944f9e28177a4a6bf759c37","tid":868349,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:35:33.000Z","msg":"本賽季早些時候，25歲的盧卡古已經領取了自己英超進球破百的證書，目前他在英超聯賽的進球數已經來到了105球，也借此超越了前輩杜奧巴。現在，盧卡古希望能向亨利的175球看齊，亨利也是在英超進球數目最多的外籍球員。<br />\n<br />\n盧卡古說道：「杜奧巴和我每天都會有溝通，這真的很棒，因為他也參與了這105球的過程。現在我在跟亨利聊了，我跟他說，我現在的目標是你的175球紀錄！」<br />\n<br />\n「我是笑著跟他說這事的，但在我的內心深處，我知道我說出這話時是超級認真的。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.standard.co.uk/sport/football/manchester-united-striker-lukaku-chasing-thierry-henry-premier-league-goal-tally-a3965836.html?amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.standard.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Fmanchester-united-striker-lukaku-chasing-thierry-henry-premier-league-goal-tally-a3965836.html%3Famp&d=WXSjg9b4xvSczAxs9sVyRdWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=0a1aba49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.standard.co.uk/sport/football/manchester-united-striker-lukaku-chasing-thierry-henry-premier-league-goal-tally-a3965836.html?amp</a>"},{"pid":"cb39198971cedb777fd289697be1fb1b7bacb4c6","tid":868349,"uid":145021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:38:40.000Z","msg":"而家先25 當佢一季廢到入得10球 32-33歲就超越亨利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85aa6240b9284d7d359c8b8e561e58e96c93ed08","tid":868349,"uid":124292,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb39198971cedb777fd289697be1fb1b7bacb4c6","tid":868349,"uid":145021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:38:40.000Z","msg":"而家先25 當佢一季廢到入得10球 32-33歲就超越亨利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:40:18.000Z","msg":"勁過亨利，獌狗就好啦，繼雲狗後又搵到神鋒"}]}